{"tid":766551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【英國品質】黑警：將軍澳戰時英軍炸彈既炸藥「好像新的一樣」","createTime":"2018-08-03T16:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T03:01:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ae142bd4b30df6feed20b5d2d78cfe79be1418f","tid":766551,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:19:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410549-20180803.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410549-20180803.htm&d=Y33Wh5SlbbBhD2ieEQzgBP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6d5a43f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410549-20180803.htm&h=1988d117\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410549-20180803.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳環保大道堆填區中午發現戰時炸彈，到晚上8時半左右，成功拆彈。<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳警區助理指揮官黃浩瀚說，一名掘泥機工人發現炸彈，警方爆炸品處理課🇨🇳🇨🇳人員🇨🇳🇨🇳到場檢驗後，證實是一枚二戰時英軍遺留的炸彈，直徑9.2吋、長1米、重300磅，由於炸彈狀態不穩定，要現場引爆，經過9小時進行3次引爆後，成功將炸彈處理。他說有關堆填區位置是處理建築廢料，相信炸彈有機會由其他地區，與填料一同運到現場。<br />\n<br />\n爆炸品處理課炸彈處理主任李展超表示，這個炸彈較厚，經過3次切割才能成功切開，形容炸藥好像新的一樣，約有50公斤高性能炸藥，一旦爆炸約500米範圍內都可感覺到強力衝擊波，100米範圍內可有人命傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n李展超說，現場上空是民航處的航道，因此處理炸彈的過程中，要短暫禁止飛機在上空飛行。"},{"pid":"ddfd626255518ca8259f1205fc702abbba92ed96","tid":766551,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"其實有幾多戰時軍火已經被非法社團收咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d277e4c7b6e53a46f956079ff2134986ba7e4689","tid":766551,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:44:34.000Z","msg":"炸彈識爆炸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇嘢啦，睇錯咗做中国<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=